Rainbow Clouds in Florida

This iridescent  magic appears when the sunrays hit very thin clouds with lots of water droplets. If the rays pass through only a few, tiny drops at a time, you’ll see this epic mini rainbow develop from the cloud. @christianservant #somewhereiwouldliketolive #Florida
